title: Project UFO 1978 - 1979 (Project Bluebook) TV Series
description:
Two agents of the U.S. Government's Project Blue Book project investigate sightings of extraterrestrials and unidentified flying objects.

Season 1 & 2 complete 26 episodes. Episode 14 actually is the last episode of series 2, if you want to watch them in order. 

This was one of my favourites when I was a kid and I couldn't get it on torrent anywhere. I have taken this off YouTube as my TV doesn't get on with the website. I have uploaded it just in case anyone is on the same boat. 

This is my first torrent, so and observations good/bad would be appreciated
